    <a name="1" id="1"></a><span class="subtitleGreen">GETTING STARTED</span>
    <br>
    <span class="main_copy_font">When you register with us, you will receive a convertible and reusable dry cleaning/garment bag (to be used for laundered shirts and dry cleaning only) as well as a laundry bag with your first scheduled pickup. Our bags are identified with a discreet barcode in the corner that will identify you as a customer. No more waiting in lines, no more waste, and better handling of your clothes.</span>
    <br>
