    <a name="2" id="2"></a><span class="subtitleGreen">FRESH SERVICE</span>
    <br>
    <span class="main_copy_font">Because nobody expects you to do your laundry at work, we don’t expect you to pick it up during working hours. With My Fresh Shirt you schedule a pick up and delivery within a 2 hour service window of your choice. Since we deliver up until 11:30 p.m., you can count on us to be there when you are. <a href="#0">back to top</a> </span>
    <br>
    <a name="3" id="3"></a>
    <span class="subtitleGreen">
        <br>
        </a>TURNAROUND TIME
    </span>
    <br>
    <span class="main_copy_font">Standard turnaround time is 2 days, and express service, where available, is typically ready within 24 hours from the time of pick up. It is up to you how we can best serve you. In the case that our professional cleaners find that an item needs special attention, we will promptly notify you via text message or e-mail detailing the concern. <a href="#0">back to top </a> </span>
    <br>
    <br>
    <a name="4" id="4"></a>
    <span class="subtitleGreen">GREEN LEAF DELIVERY </span>
    <br>
    <span class="main_copy_font">Our Eco-Logic technology makes it easy for you to schedule your pick-up and delivery during the same time window as your neighbor.  Scheduling your service in these windows helps us minimize our carbon emission levels by eliminating wasteful trips to and from our facility.  When you schedule your pick-up or delivery during these highlighted times, you will receive valuable eco-logic points, which may be redeemed for various promotions or charitable donations. Choose a green leaf service window today and leave the other time slots envy of the green. <a href="#0">back to top </a> </span>
    <br>
    <br>
    <a name="5" id="5"></a>
    <span class="subtitleGreen">DOORMAN SERVICE</span>
    <br>
    <span class="main_copy_font">If you live in a doorman building, doing your dry cleaning and laundry couldn’t be easier.  Simply schedule your pick up and delivery on the dates you desire and then leave your clothes with your doorman.  Or, if your building is registered with My Fresh Shirt, you don’t have to go through the standard ordering process.  Just leave your laundry with your doorman, and we’ll pick it up and deliver it on your building’s scheduled days of service.  We encourage you to contact us with any questions you may have regarding our doorman policies and procedures, at <a href="mailto:customerservice@myfreshshirt.com">customerservice@myfreshshirt.com</a>.
<br/><br/>

If your doorman building is not registered, speak with your building manager and register it today. No special commitment is required!  <a href="#0">back to top </a> </span>
